name: JetCityGuide
0:
”Alexa, open Jet City Guide.”
”Where can I go to party?”
”I want some coffee.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: jet city guide
des: This is a simple guide that randomly selects from a list of Jake's favorites when given a category to choose from. Looking for a lunch recommendation? Then open Jet City Guide and say "lunch" to hear about one of Jake's favorite spots for a sandwich or maybe a burger. If you want to hear about some sight-seeing options, just say "recommend an attraction" to hear some good places to visit while you're in town. And since rain is always a possibility here, better make sure to say "go outside" to get a quick weather update.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
